OL,3,CMan stuck with car he can't drive as
OL,4,CCitroen issue 'do not drive' order
OL,6,FA man has criticised car manufacturer
OL,7,FCitroen saying that his vehicle is a
OL,8,F'death trap' after potentially serious
OL,9,Ffaults were found with airbags in some
OL,10,Fmodels.
OL,12,FPeter Bailey, 71, from Flintshire, has
OL,13,Fbeen told not to drive his Citroen C3
OL,14,Fafter a potentially dangerous airbag
OL,15,Ffault. He is one of tens of thousands
OL,16,Fof customers in the UK understood to
OL,17,Fbe potentially affected by the fault.
