OL,3,CMan stuck with car he can't drive as
OL,4,CCitroen issue 'do not drive' order
OL,6,FMr Bailey who suffers with C0PD and
OL,7,FType 2 diabetes says he is facing a
OL,8,Ftwo month wait to get his car repaired
OL,9,Fand is struggling to get to medical
OL,10,Fappointments.
OL,12,F"I've been driving around in a death
OL,13,Ftrap. It's ridiculous, you don't
OL,14,Fexpect this from Citroen, or any other
OL,15,Fcar manufacturer."
OL,17,F"I was driving at risk, I take my
OL,18,Fgrandchildren in this. If we had an
OL,19,Faccident and the airbag went off and
OL,20,Fkilled my grandchild it would break my
OL,21,Fheart, it would kill me."
