OL,3,CMan stuck with car he can't drive as
OL,4,CCitroen issue 'do not drive' order
OL,6,FMr Bailey said he had no idea about
OL,7,Fthe fault with the airbags until he
OL,8,Freceived a letter telling him not to
OL,9,Fdrive his vehicle.
OL,11,FThe vehicles affected are second-
OL,12,Fgeneration Citroen C3s produced from
OL,13,F2009 to 2016 and first-generation DS3s
OL,14,Fmanufactured from 2016 to 2019.
OL,16,FThe French firm has issued a 'Stop-
OL,17,FDrive' order after a recent report
OL,18,Fstated that a woman sustained fatal
OL,19,Finjuries caused by an airbag in a 2014
OL,20,FCitroen C3 in Reims, France, last year.
