OL,3,CMan stuck with car he can't drive as
OL,4,CCitroen issue 'do not drive' order
OL,6,FAs a result, around 82,000 C3 and DS3
OL,7,Fmodels have been removed from the road
OL,8,Facross France. The fault is understood
OL,9,Fto mean that the airbags can explode
OL,10,Funcontrollably causing injuries.
OL,12,FThe vehicles use Takata airbag
OL,13,Fsystems, which could be faulty.
OL,14,FHowever, airbag manufacturers
OL,15,FStellantis UK said that there were no
OL,16,Freported incidents of faults in the
OL,17,FUK, but it has decided to take action
OL,18,Fregardless.
