OL,3,CMan stuck with car he can't drive as
OL,4,CCitroen issue 'do not drive' order
OL,6,FThey said: "Stellantis UK is
OL,7,Fmobilising its full network of
OL,8,Fsuppliers, retailers and manufacturing
OL,9,Fplant to support this action to ensure
OL,10,Fthe fastest, safest and most
OL,11,Fconvenient solution for each customer.
OL,12,FStellantis remains fully committed to
OL,13,Facting swiftly, transparently, and
OL,14,Fresponsibly in addressing this issue."
