OL,3,CMan stuck with car he can't drive as
OL,4,CCitroen issue 'do not drive' order
OL,6,FIn a letter sent to affected
OL,7,Fcustomers, Citroen said: "As you might
OL,8,Fhave heard from the media, Takata
OL,9,Fairbag inflators are being recalled
OL,10,Fglobally due to a serious safety risk.
OL,11,FThese inflators can degrade over time
OL,12,Fand, in the event of an accident, may
OL,13,Frupture with excessive force. This can
OL,14,Fcause severe injuries or even death."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/13
