OL,3,CMan stuck with car he can't drive as
OL,4,CCitroen issue 'do not drive' order
OL,6,FThe letter went on to add: "Due to the
OL,7,Fserious safety risk involved, we are
OL,8,Fnow taking stronger measures and
OL,9,Furgently ask you to STOP DRIVING YOUR
OL,10,FVEHICLE IMMEDIATELY until the airbags
OL,11,Fhave been replaced. This replacement
OL,12,Ftakes 2 hours and is free of charge."
OL,14,FHowever Mr Bailey says other than the
OL,15,Fletter he has had no other
OL,16,Fcommunication from Citroen and cannot
OL,17,Fget his vehicle repaired until
OL,18,FSeptember and that will be at a garage
OL,19,Fin Prestatyn - over 20 miles from his
OL,20,Fhome.
