OL,3,CMan stuck with car he can't drive as
OL,4,CCitroen issue 'do not drive' order
OL,6,F"How do I get it there? I'm on a
OL,7,Fpension I can't afford a tow-truck to
OL,8,Ftake it there so I've got to take a
OL,9,Fchance and drive it there," he said.
OL,11,F"I've got a car here I can't drive.
OL,12,FI'm paying insurance, paying tax on
OL,13,Fit, and it's stuck here and nobody
OL,14,Fseems to want to do anything about it.
OL,15,FIf I could go back in time I wouldn't
OL,16,Feven buy the car."
OL,18,FWhile he waits to get his car returned
OL,19,Fhe says he is relying on his son to
OL,20,Ftake him to medical appointments or
OL,21,Fhas to use his family's vehicles.
