OL,3,CMan stuck with car he can't drive as
OL,4,CCitroen issue 'do not drive' order
OL,6,F"It's not just inconveniencing me it's
OL,7,Finconveniencing him (his son). It's
OL,8,Fdisgusting. The least they could do is
OL,9,Fget the garage to give us a courtesy
OL,10,Fcar."
OL,12,FIn a statement, Stellantis ` the
OL,13,Fparent company of Citroen - said: "The
OL,14,FCompany's focus is on completing the
OL,15,Freplacement of airbags in affected
OL,16,Fvehicles as swiftly as possible.
OL,17,FWorking hand in hand with our Citroen
OL,18,FRetailer Network, we are working to
OL,19,Fmaximise the number of vehicles we can
OL,20,Frepair every day.
