OL,6,F"To increase our repair capacity
OL,7,Ffurther, work is ongoing to introduce
OL,8,Fadditional airbag replacement sites at
OL,9,Fconvenient locations as well as repair-
OL,10,Fat-home options. It is inevitable,
OL,11,Fwith such a large number of vehicles
OL,12,Faffected, that customers will be
OL,13,Finconvenienced in the short term.
OL,15,F"However, we are deploying a variety
OL,16,Fof options to support mobility,
OL,17,Frecognising that every driver will
OL,18,Fhave individual requirements, and that
OL,19,Fpriority needs to be given to
OL,20,Fcustomers with the most urgent needs."
